â€œTook a trip to LA and came up on this strain. It was an almost immediate hit. A twilight sedation due to the time of day it was.. anyway I loved it and its perfect to smoke and unwind from a long day. Taste is good also. Now to try and find it in Phoenix, we'll see.â€

â€œFor all you Indica lovers out there, this is a 100% pure Indica. This is the best strain I have ever used for my depression, stress, and mainly INSOMNIA.
